Aerosmith - 1975-08-29 - Central Park, NY (Soundboard)
Live at the Schaeffer Music Festival in Central Park, NY.
This is a FM broadcast from the King Biscuit Flower Hour and the track list features songs from Aerosmith's first three albums and it's pretty enjoyable.

Pre-FM - Unofficial soundboard recording - excellent quality
